<HEADLINE> (Urgent) Annan to Start Visit to Germany, Russia on Kosovo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, April 19 (Xinhua) -- U.N. Secretary-General
Kofi Annan is scheduled to pay a visit to Germany and Russia on
Kosovo, a Serbian province, U.N. spokesman Fred Eckhard announced
Monday.
</P>
<P>
Annan will also appoint a special envoy on Kosovo, but the name
remains unknown at the moment, diplomatic sources said. 
</P>
