instability, which will in turn lead to a war between Muslims and
non-Muslims," he added.
</P>
<P>
This is the second blast that hit the Indonesian capital within
five days.
</P>
<P>
A powerful bomb exploded and badly damaged a shop at Jakarta's
Hayam Wuruk Plaza shopping center last Thursday, injuring several
people.  
