The U.S. General, who will stay here for two days, was met at
the airport by Pakistan's Chairman of Joint Chiefs of Staff
Committee and Chief of Army Staff General Pervez Musharraf.
</P>
<P>
Zinnie will hold talks with Musharraf on wide array of
subjects, especially the Pak-U.S. military cooperation and
regional situation, according to informed sources.
