develop cooperation and forge interaction between the armed forces
of the two countries.
</P>
<P>
Despite several ups and downs in the Pak-U.S. relations, the
military leadership of the two countries has always been in touch
with each other.
</P>
<P>
The current visit by General Zinnie has also provided an
opportunity for the two sides to discuss the latest development in
the South Asian region. 
