Minister Hun Sen, to provide Cambodia with a low interest loan of
150 million yuan (about 18 million dollars) and grant aid of 40
million yuan.
</P>
<P>
China also agreed in principle to grant Cambodia commercial
loans of 200 million dollars for agriculture and infrastructure
projects.
