<HEADLINE> Hang Seng China Enterprises Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 20 (Xinhua) -- Hang Seng China Enterprises
Index rose 15.18 points to close at 438.80 on Tuesday.
