a U.S. military training facility in the village of Kunigami at
around 9:45 p.m. local time (1245 GMT) Monday, the report said.
</P>
<P>
U.S. military helicopters and Japan's Maritime Safety Agency
patrol boats are searching the vicinity of the crash site for the
missing crew member and the helicopter's wreck, which has not yet
been found.
</P>
