<DOCNO> XIE19990420.0176 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-20 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chain Store Sales Exceed 100 Billion Yuan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 20 (Xinhua) -- China's booming chain store
industry recorded 100 billion yuan (12 billion US dollars) in
sales last year, up 70 percent on an annual basis, according to a
recent report released by the China Internal Trade Bureau and
Chain Store Association.
</P>
<P>
The 1998 sales volume for supermarkets, convenience stores and
large warehouse stores hit 60 billion yuan, up 43 percent on 1997.
</P>
<P>
China has 71 chain store enterprises with annual sales
exceeding 100 million yuan.
</P>
<P>
Total 1998 retail sales of consumer goods stood at 2,900
billion yuan, up 6.8 percent on 1997.
</P>
<P>
Zha Lihua, an official with China Internal Trade Bureau, noted
that chain store corporations have adopted measures including
mergers, restructuring, acquisitions and partnerships in recent
years. Related measures enabled the corporations to expand their
scale and effectively use the tangible resources of small chain
stores.
</P>
<P>
Thirty-seven of 121 enterprises with annual sales exceeding 50
million yuan were partnership chain stores, up 6.7 percent on 1997.
</P>
<P>
Zha pointed to the declining annual sales of large department
stores and the rapid growth of the chain store industry has
injected vigor into the retail sales industry.
</P>
<P>
She added that China's rural market offer vast consumption
potential. However, according to Zha, the shortage of goods
suitable to the rural market and inconvenient transportation has
limited efforts to tap existing potential
</P>
<P>
China has introduced concrete measures to accelerate the reform
of sales patterns in order to stimulate domestic consumption, and
will further develop the rural market potential by establishing
chain stores and expanding sales outlets.
</P>
<P>
Analysts further noted that strengthening management over the
trade and wholesale markets will help fuel growth of the chain
store industry.  
</P>
</TEXT>
