<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, April 20 (Xinhua) -- In a recent comprehensive
survey conducted by an Italian travel trade publication, Dubai
emerged as a close second to Paris as the best incentive tourist
destination in the world.
</P>
<P>
The publication named In Viaggio surveyed numerous popular
destinations around the world and it ranked Dubai second to Paris
as the best incentive destination.
</P>
<P>
