<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, April 20 (Xinhua) -- A private helicopter crashed
Tuesday in the open field of a national prison camp near Manila,
injuring three people, one of them seriously, police said.
</P>
<P>
Police said sketchy reports showed that the helicopter crashed
on its way from Manila to Cavite, the northern Philippines, at
11:30 (03:30 GMT).
</P>
<P>
