<TEXT>
<P>
LIMA, April 19 (Xinhua) -- The Andean Community (CAN) will hold
a seminar on Tuesday in Ottawa, Canada, to promote trade and
investment with the member states of the North American Free Trade
Agreement (NAFTA).
</P>
