Organization (NATO) has requested Romania to give NATO "unlimited
access to its sky," and Romanian President Emil Constantinescu
will discuss the issue with leaders of different parties on
Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Romania will make its response at a top meeting of national
defense committee after the president's Tuesday discussion.
</P>
